{"tid":1657611,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[發現定律] 只要套戲唔喺支國上映 劇本就會正常甚至出息","createTime":"2019-10-16T07:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T10:19:08.000Z","uid":84081,"like":65,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"5d7e091e6b5918dc39ed439577b04f61a252aa13","tid":1657611,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:25:49.000Z","msg":"John Wick 同 Joker <br />\n兩套野都係比較low budget<br />\n唔駛喺支國上黎回本<br />\n<br />\n結果係咩？<br />\n<br />\nJohn Wick 3<br />\nBudget: 75 million <br />\nBox office: 323 million<br />\n<br />\nJoker<br />\nBudget: 70 million<br />\nBox office: 556 million + on going<br />\n<br />\n反而<br />\n李安套Gemini <br />\nBudget: 150 million<br />\nBox office: 超過50million都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>導演勁、演員唔差 個個屌劇本差</strong><br />\n點解？<br />\n因為高budeget戲多數老闆會play safe <br />\n想喺大陸上影回本<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但喺大陸上影就好多限制 啲劇本左改右改<br />\n最後拖到一定要開戲 就改到不倫不類<br />\n<br />\n我大膽講句<br />\n未來戰士新一集如果大陸有得上<br />\n好大機會劇本唔會好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然荷里活有人可以寫到劇本又好又過到大陸審批<br />\n但數量有幾多呢？<br />\n我暫時諗唔到<br />\n<br />\n結論：下次想知套戲好冇睇 睇下支國上唔上畫 唔上就大機會啲好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea15d3ffc3e0e028c512d5bc51bad8964332b85","tid":1657611,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:26:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHn4YGm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHn4YGm.jpg&h=a9bf801a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9c2a4b1a76a055d366218e4b181d7957b31da4c6","tid":1657611,"uid":84081,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:28:45.000Z","msg":"Box office =/= 好睇<br />\n<br />\n我只係想指出遷就大陸令人隨時蝕本<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1f09aa302a8f6132349f878c088e4e347df91d1","tid":1657611,"uid":260292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:30:48.000Z","msg":"師兄心水清"},{"pid":"350269c0c0369f7a58ed6787eb3481fcb781b9dd","tid":1657611,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1f09aa302a8f6132349f878c088e4e347df91d1","tid":1657611,"uid":260292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:30:48.000Z","msg":"師兄心水清"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:53:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516b6a9d458d9105069de8af3a2483bf89cc1530","tid":1657611,"uid":295602,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:01:54.000Z","msg":"雖然係事實,<br />\n但係攞李安黎做例子又有少少不公嘅, 佢太過追求試新技術,<br />\n今次gemini係滿足到佢試技術野, 但係個劇本故仔主題已經好過時<br />\n<br />\n可以睇番Pacific Rim, 第一集堪稱經典<br />\n第二集加入景甜企圖賺人仔<br />\n承繼唔到個靈魂之餘, 成個故仔乜鳩元素都加入去, 最後變一pat亂七八糟嘅視覺混沌"},{"pid":"24ec00081e3066b66ec912c58da72e00e4f03373","tid":1657611,"uid":84081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"516b6a9d458d9105069de8af3a2483bf89cc1530","tid":1657611,"uid":295602,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:01:54.000Z","msg":"雖然係事實,<br />\n但係攞李安黎做例子又有少少不公嘅, 佢太過追求試新技術,<br />\n今次gemini係滿足到佢試技術野, 但係個劇本故仔主題已經好過時<br />\n<br />\n可以睇番Pacific Rim, 第一集堪稱經典<br />\n第二集加入景甜企圖賺人仔<br />\n承繼唔到個靈魂之餘, 成個故仔乜鳩元素都加入去, 最後變一pat亂七八糟嘅視覺混沌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:05:45.000Z","msg":"呢句真<br />\n清仲清晰過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec44e3302d4aac7348dcb67709740d67a65e0ca0","tid":1657611,"uid":140831,"like":1,"dislike":24,"score":-23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:06:50.000Z","msg":"John wick3垃圾到中場閃人wo ching"},{"pid":"2bb414266b13cf4bede9804fb1bf58bc15f5108d","tid":1657611,"uid":84081,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"ec44e3302d4aac7348dcb67709740d67a65e0ca0"